# Chat Completions & Messages API

Nanobridge exposes both OpenAI Chat Completions and Anthropic Messages. Upstream traffic is routed to Tencent Hunyuan model backends.

---

## OpenAI — Chat Completions

**Path**: `POST /chat/completions` or `POST /v1/chat/completions`

**Example base URL**: `https://api.nanobridge.net/v1`

**Auth**: `Authorization: Bearer <API_KEY>`

### Common request fields

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `model` | string | Model ID; default recommendation is `deepseek-v4-flash` |
| `messages` | array | Message list (required); each item has `role` and `content` |
| `stream` | boolean | Enable streaming; default `false` |
| `temperature` | number | Sampling temperature (optional) |
| `max_tokens` | integer | Max tokens to generate (optional) |

### Non-streaming response (OpenAI shape)

```json
{
  "id": "chatcmpl-xxx",
  "object": "chat.completion",
  "choices": [{
    "index": 0,
    "message": { "role": "assistant", "content": "..." },
    "finish_reason": "stop"
  }],
  "usage": {
    "prompt_tokens": 12,
    "completion_tokens": 8,
    "total_tokens": 20
  }
}
```

### cURL

```bash
curl https://api.nanobridge.net/v1/chat/completions \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -d '{
    "model": "deepseek-v4-flash",
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Hello!"}]
  }'
```

### Streaming

Set `"stream": true`. The response is OpenAI-style SSE.

